==English==

===Etymology===
From {{L.}} ''connectere'' "to fasten together," from (com-) "together" + ''nectere'' "to bind, tie."

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɛkt|-ɛkt]]

===Transitive verb===
{{en-verb}}
#to join two pieces
#to join an electrical or telephone line

